24:47.697 --> 24:49.940
excited about it. And who picked this particular 
area for research? Was it the university, or was it

24:52.743 --> 24:55.827
the schools, or was it done jointly? It was kind of 
done jointly, but I would say primarily the

24:55.847 --> 24:58.550
schools. We wanted to do something that was more 
action-oriented that they felt that they needed.

